{"id":12283,"type":2,"name":"L'illusionniste","name_cn":"魔术师","date":"2010-06-16","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/94/55/12283_mSdoj.jpg","rating":{"rank":418,"total":310,"count":{"1":2,"2":1,"3":0,"4":1,"5":4,"6":16,"7":67,"8":133,"9":70,"10":16},"score":7.9},"summary":"        20世纪50年代末期，曾经风靡一时的剧场风云变幻，人们迷恋电视、迷恋摇滚，对于曾经伴随他们长大的各种杂耍则不再关注。他是一个经验丰富的魔术师，舞台上得体从容，现实中却不得不为了可怜的生活费而流转于各个表演场所，上至华贵的音乐厅，下至破落偏僻的小酒馆，不变的是他对魔术的执着。在苏格兰某个乡间逗留时，魔术师结识了一个小女孩，她感叹于那些神奇的魔法，于是偷偷离开故乡，转而追随魔术师的脚步。他们辗转来至爱丁堡，生活变得愈加艰辛，而为了满足女孩对魔法的信任和对繁华世界的向往，魔术师不得不想各种办法去赚钱……","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>魔术师</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/15914\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">Sylvain Chomet</a></li><li><span>分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/23360\">鈴木亜矢</a></li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/23360\">鈴木亜矢</a></li><li><span>第二原画: </span><a href=\"/person/23360\">鈴木亜矢</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>The Illusionist</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>魔幻师</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>魔法玩家</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>幻术师</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>幻术家</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>イリュージョニスト</li><li><span>上映年度: </span>2010年6月16日</li><li><span>片长: </span>77分钟</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.lillusionniste-lefilm.com/</li><li><span>动画制作: </span>PATHE</li><li><span>编剧: </span>Sylvain Chomet、Jacques Tati</li>","collection":{"on_hold":29,"dropped":24,"wish":269,"collect":448,"doing":13},"tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":100},{"name":"法国","count":84},{"name":"欧美","count":62},{"name":"2010","count":59},{"name":"动画电影","count":36},{"name":"治愈","count":13},{"name":"原创","count":10},{"name":"映画","count":10},{"name":"致郁","count":4},{"name":"剧场","count":2},{"name":"2010-2019","count":2},{"name":"","count":""}],"eps":[{"id":844877,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/844877","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":""}],"staff":[{"id":15914,"image":"//lain.